texts.text: Tobias Ahlin is the lead experience designer at Mojang Studios. He joined the company on January 2, 2017.[1] Before joining Mojang, he also developed for companies such as Spotify and GitHub.
"Hello new adventure! So excited today to join @Kappische @jeb_ @vubui and many more at @Mojang to make great things for @Minecraft" – @tobiasahlin on Twitter, January 2, 2017
